{"tid":93842,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩慘得過垃圾屋企人","createTime":"2017-01-24T17:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T21:48:04.000Z","uid":79200,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14d779ecac66c5aed55a59c004ac9a6b471d11ed","tid":93842,"uid":79200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"我老豆係做裝修，失咗業四年，上年年中先肯岀黎做野，做足四年廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老母會有時做下陪月pt <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩老就有一個共同點就係佢地講野勁鐘意得罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講下背景，我讀梗大學chur科日日8點放 冇dayoff <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇時間返pt，而屋企人淨係肯比2000一個月我除返每日得60幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本連食飯都唔夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屋企人又問我借成6000蚊，過咗半年都未還<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講野又成日單單打打話我廢 唔夠其他人叻 將我同其他人比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有時要買下教科書問佢拎錢仲慘過去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呢咖追佢還錢，佢地竟然屌返我理財有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話要分六期還，一個月還一期咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我家姐啱啱大學grad 就被逼比月月俾5000家用，但我屋企人都覺得太少 日日罵佢，我真係唔想做下一個家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題係，佢地明明有樓，個個月有家用收，自己又有翻工，仲日日扮窮俾多少少錢我都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就黎食飯都冇錢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解佢地咁撚自私咁撚狗，完全唔係做埋老豆老母嘅角色，眼見其他同學個個屋企人都俾夠錢自己 至少有三餐溫飽 我真係好唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我應該點樣做啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4428b40751463c3a840f87ae15c178ed6d8840a","tid":93842,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:51:21.000Z","msg":"神科?"